ActFederal-Provincial Fiscal Arrangements Act
SubjectOrder Amending Schedule l to the Federal-Provincial Fiscal Arrangements Act
PrecisOrder Amending SCHEDULE I OF THE FEDERAL-PROVINCIAL FISCAL ARRANGEMENTS ACT in order to 1) add the Oshawa Port Authority and the Vancouver Fraser Port Authority for the purpose of clarifying their obligations related to the payment of provincial sales tax and/or other provincial taxes and fees; and (2) delete the Vancouver Port Authority, the Fraser River Port Authority and the North Fraser Port Authority since they no longer exist.
RegistrationRegistration: SOR/ 2014-0028 Publication Date: 2014-02-26
